data.description: Price improvement!!!! Welcome home to this charming 3 bedroom 2 bathroom completely updated home in sunny Clearwater, Florida. Conveniently located just minutes from golf-cart friendly downtown Dunedin where there is no shortage of shopping and dining. This homes location is also close to the Pinellas Trail, Dunedin Blue Jays spring training stadium, Seminole boat ramp and just a few minutes' drive to one of Florida's top beaches, Clearwater Beach. Upon entering the home you will be greeted with plenty of natural light shining into the open living room, dining room and kitchen starring brand new laminate flooring. The kitchen is updated with wood shaker cabinets accented by granite countertops and timeless subway tile backsplash as well as all stainless-steel appliances featuring an electric cook top with a stainless-steel hooded vent. The bedrooms are split floor plan with the primary on the left side of the home and the 2 additional bedrooms and guest bathroom on the right side of the home. The primary bedroom has its own ensuite bathroom which has been completely updated (2021) with beautiful tile walk in shower and large vanity with granite countertop. The brand new front loader washer and dryer are conveniently tucked away in the primary bathroom closet. The guest bathroom has also been updated (2021) and features tub/shower combo with granite countertop vanity. Step out of the back doors onto the large back deck which is perfect for relaxing or entertaining and overlooks your oversized fenced in back yard. There is also a large shed in the back yard that is perfect for storage or an eventual workshop or workspace. New AC 2021, new hot water heater 2021, NO HOA, NON Flood zone. This home offers everything you have been searching for. Don't hesitate and call to schedule a private tour today!!
